cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with the problem of spatiotemporal localisation and classification of actions in videos, which is a core problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories as well. Additionally, the paper deals with video analysis, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) categories.
